The paper deals with transfer learning, which is a subfield of machine learning (cs.LG). The proposed method involves learning shared subspaces for both domains, which suggests the use of techniques from computer vision (cs.CV) and natural language processing (cs.CL). The paper also mentions the use of spam email data set, which falls under information retrieval (cs.IR) and the use of face expression data set, which falls under artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
